Texts.Chs: 一扇基础的飞船门，在这种情况下它不会打开。
Texts.Eng: A basic ship door. It won't open at the moment.

Texts.Chs: 一扇门，现在它似乎不能打开。
Texts.Eng: A door. It appears to be disabled currently.

Texts.Chs: 很酷的门，糟糕的是它现在不能打开。
Texts.Eng: Cool door. Too bad it isn't opening right now.

Texts.Chs: 这扇门坏了，显然在一段时间内不能被打开。
Texts.Eng: The door is broken, it ain't opening any time soon.

Texts.Chs: 这种门在我们猿族的飞船上被使用。这一个工作异常。
Texts.Eng: These doors are used on all our ships. This one is not playing nice.
